beer.beer_description: The tropical citrus and pineapple flavours of this beast are a set to take you straight to your happy place. We hop it up with a hit of Ella at the beginning of the boil, but it’s the late introduction of Vic Secret that takes you to the heart of the flavor profile. We’ve balanced our hop bitterness with a malt profile that is evident, but not dominant to make the beer approachable, sessionable, and damn tasty!
